    "Name": "Grand Sentinel GST-1X",
    "Details": "The GST-1X is Defiance Industries' 500th anniversary tribute to the original Sentinel, scaling the concept up to 60 tons with significantly more capable weapons across the board. A Rotary AC/5 and Streak SRM 6 form the core damage output while twin ER Medium Lasers extend its reach. MASC pushes it past 100 kph in bursts and sixteen tons of Ballistic-Reinforced armor makes it considerably tougher than its weight class suggests.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
